com.hazelcast.internal.util.futures

Class ChainingFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.AbstractCompletableFuture<T>
      • com.hazelcast.internal.util.futures.ChainingFuture<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompletableFuture<T>, Future<T>

    public class ChainingFuture<T>
extends AbstractCompletableFuture<T>
    Iterates over supplied ICompletableFuture serially. It advances to the next future only when the previous future is completed. It completes when there is no other future available.
